1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,633
The confirmation link opens the customer verification wizard for this booking code.

2
00:00:03,633 --> 00:00:07,267
Start with the rental summary and continue only if the booking code, dates, vehicle, and total look right.

3
00:00:07,267 --> 00:00:10,900
The customer scans the license barcode when possible, or uses manual entry if camera scan is unavailable.

4
00:00:10,900 --> 00:00:14,533
Manual entry is the fallback when scanning is not available.

5
00:00:14,533 --> 00:00:18,167
Enter the legal street address.

6
00:00:18,167 --> 00:00:21,800
Enter city.

7
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:25,433
Select the customer state.

8
00:00:25,433 --> 00:00:29,067
Enter date of birth for verification.

9
00:00:29,067 --> 00:00:32,700
Continue after address and date of birth are complete.

10
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:36,333
Enter the driver license number.

11
00:00:36,333 --> 00:00:39,967
Select the issuing state.

12
00:00:39,967 --> 00:00:43,600
Enter license expiration.

13
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:47,233
License photos are optional, but they speed up admin verification and pickup.

14
00:00:47,233 --> 00:00:50,867
Continue after license fields are complete.

15
00:00:50,867 --> 00:00:54,500
Open and read the full terms before accepting.

16
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:58,133
Accept terms only after scrolling to the end.

17
00:00:58,133 --> 00:01:01,767
Continue after terms are accepted.

18
00:01:01,767 --> 00:01:05,400
Every acknowledgement must be checked before the signature step.

19
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:09,033
Continue after all acknowledgements are checked.

20
00:01:09,033 --> 00:01:12,667
Typed signature is available when drawing is not ideal.

21
00:01:12,667 --> 00:01:16,300
Type the customer legal signature.

22
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:19,933
Continue to insurance after signature is saved.

23
00:01:19,933 --> 00:01:23,567
Choose personal insurance or Bonzah coverage before review.

24
00:01:23,567 --> 00:01:27,200
Enter insurance company.

25
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:30,833
Enter policy number.

26
00:01:30,833 --> 00:01:34,467
Enter policy expiration.

27
00:01:34,467 --> 00:01:38,100
Continue to review; payment is still gated by approval.

28
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:41,733
Review the itemized package before submitting for approval.

29
00:01:41,733 --> 00:01:45,367
Submit the completed package for admin approval.

30
00:01:45,367 --> 00:01:49,000
The customer waits here until admin approval unlocks payment.
